{"sn1.9:0.1":"Samyutta Nikaya 1.9 ","sn1.9:0.2":"1. Nalavagga ","sn1.9:0.3":"Manakamasutta ","sn1.9:1.1":"Savatthinidanam. ","sn1.9:1.2":"Ekamantam thita kho sa devata bhagavato santike imam gatham abhasi: ","sn1.9:2.1":"“Na manakamassa damo idhatthi, ","sn1.9:2.2":"Na monamatthi asamahitassa; ","sn1.9:2.3":"Eko aranne viharam pamatto, ","sn1.9:2.4":"Na maccudheyyassa tareyya paran”ti. ","sn1.9:3.1":"“Manam pahaya susamahitatto, ","sn1.9:3.2":"Sucetaso sabbadhi vippamutto; ","sn1.9:3.3":"Eko aranne viharam appamatto, ","sn1.9:3.4":"Sa maccudheyyassa tareyya paran”ti. "}